name: Re structured art
description:
Procedural structure based on a specific art piece from a wallet address, the art used as input is analyzed to sort colors by magnitudes and contrasts, the number of editions sold determines the number of color clusters present, the wallet address is also used as a seed seed for randomization, this image is a structured 3D image of an image.

Test walled adress 
2500x3200px - Generative art collection by Itu.
